Description: full-featured configurable e-switch firmware for tiny45/85
  2017-10-16 r1.2: http://budgetlightforum.com/comment/1207608#comment-1207608
  Manuals: http://budgetlightforum.com/node/55296
  Old Narsil below:
    2017-05-29 r1.0: http://budgetlightforum.com/node/54635
