    2016-03-21 rev: http://budgetlightforum.com/comment/915711#comment-915711
Authors: Tom E, ToyKeeper, JonnyC
MCU: attiny45, attiny85
Button-Type: momentary
Memory: configurable
Modes: ramp, config, tactical strobe, police strobe, bike flasher, beacon,
  alpine beacon, battcheck, tempcheck, voltage readout, soft lock, momentary
Extras: mode groups, ramping UI, thermal step-down, LVP,
  indicator LED, dual PWM, triple PWM, turbo timer
